"Per-core" = "各核心";
"P = Performance cores (faster, higher power). E = Efficiency cores (slower, lower power). macOS assigns which core handles each workload automatically. On Intel Macs all cores are equivalent and show as Core N." = "P = 性能核心（速度更快，功耗更高）。E = 能效核心（速度较慢，功耗更低）。macOS 会自动分配由哪个核心处理各项任务。在 Intel Mac 上，所有核心都是等效的，统一显示为 Core N。";
"Core %ld" = "核心 %ld";
"Thermal Pressure" = "热压力";
"This is the macOS thermal throttling signal — not an exact temperature reading.\n\n• Nominal: No throttling. System running normally.\n• Fair: Slight throttling may be occurring.\n• Serious: Active throttling. Performance is being reduced to cool the system.\n• Critical: Severe throttling. Immediate action recommended (close apps, remove from enclosed spaces).\n\nExact die temperatures (CPU/GPU) are not readable on Apple Silicon without a privileged kernel extension. macOS blocks SMC access for user-space apps." = "这是 macOS 的热节流信号 —— 并非精确的温度读数。\n\n• 标称：无节流。系统运行正常。\n• 一般：可能出现轻微节流。\n• 严重：正在主动节流。性能正被降低以为系统降温。\n• 危急：严重节流。建议立即采取措施（关闭应用、移出封闭空间）。\n\n在 Apple Silicon 上，若无特权内核扩展则无法读取精确的芯片温度（CPU/GPU）。macOS 会阻止用户空间应用访问 SMC。";
