"macOS reports four thermal pressure levels:\n\n• Nominal — system operating normally.\n• Fair — some power reduction to prevent overheating.\n• Serious — significant throttling in effect.\n• Critical — aggressive throttling; performance severely impacted.\n\nThis is read from ProcessInfo.thermalState — the same value macOS uses internally to throttle workloads." = "macOS 会报告四种热压力级别：\n\n• 标称 —— 系统运行正常。\n• 一般 —— 略微降低功耗以防止过热。\n• 严重 —— 正在进行明显节流。\n• 危急 —— 强力节流；性能受到严重影响。\n\n此数据读取自 ProcessInfo.thermalState —— 与 macOS 内部用于对工作负载进行节流的数值相同。";

